## Future Plans

Please include here

- We are partnered with QPR FC to create a new way they can engage fans with the club's history, IRL operations and expand their online activities. This partnership is looking long term at growing their global fanbase and expanding on the activities available to current members. Both companies have resources dedicated to the operations of this project. We have a list of collaborations we will be rolling into the project along with activations with the QPR FC sponsors.
- We have joint marketing efforts to expand and grow the project and are actively seeking collaborators and sponsors to become involved.


